# Shared Agent Context

This file contains common context loaded by all agents.

## Project

- **Name:** ${PROJECT_NAME}
- **Sprint Status:** `sprint/current-sprint.yaml`
- **Active Work:** `.session/{story-id}-session.md`
- **Agent Framework:** Pennyfarthing (npm)

### Tech Stack

| Component | Language | Framework |
|-----------|----------|-----------|
| Example | TypeScript | Node.js |

### Repo Structure

```
${PROJECT_NAME}/
├── src/                    # Source code
├── tests/                  # Tests
├── docs/                   # Documentation
├── sprint/                 # Sprint YAML files
├── scripts/                # Utility scripts
└── .claude/                # Claude Code configuration
    ├── core/               # Pennyfarthing core (managed)
    ├── project/            # Project-specific config
    │   ├── agents/         # Agent sidecars (project knowledge)
    │   ├── docs/           # This file, agent-scopes.yaml
    │   └── hooks/          # setup-env.sh
    ├── skills/             # Core skills (managed)
    ├── personas/           # Persona themes (managed)
    └── manifest.json       # Pennyfarthing version tracking
```

## Git Branch Strategy

- **All work:** Feature branches
- **Branch from:** `develop` (or `main` if no develop branch)
- **PRs target:** `develop`
- **Naming:** `feat/[story]-[description]` or `fix/[issue]-[description]`

## TDD Workflow

1. **SM** creates story and hands off to TEA
2. **TEA** writes failing tests, hands off to Dev
3. **Dev** implements to pass tests, hands off to Reviewer
4. **Reviewer** reviews code, approves or requests changes

## Testing Commands

```bash
# Run tests
npm test

# Run specific test
npm test -- --grep "test name"
```

## Building

```bash
# Build
npm run build

# Type check
npm run typecheck
```
